      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Thin maiden. RHINESTONE RORY (3) returns and while he's had plenty of looks, this is one of his easiest assignments yet. Has good tactical speed and should give a bold sight. HIGH ALTITUDE (11) was poised to strike when resuming here three weeks ago but just lacked a fitness edge late. Better for that but will need a smart ride from the wide draw. GREEN AMBER (10) was much better here last start when showing early muster and fighting on for second. Peak fitness now and should give herself every chance again on speed. NORENSON (8) was flat when resuming here three weeks ago but is open to sharp improvement with the blinkers applied.",
